rows.name: Ask Fozimure about recent developments.

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0001
rows.name:
I volunteered as a BLADE mechanic because I wanted to
do anything I could to aid you humans, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0002
rows.name:
Every little bit helps, right? And in that spirit,
I've taken up mimeosome maintenance in addition to
my my usual Skell repair duties. But...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0003
rows.name:
Those mimeosomes are... Well, the technology is
astonishing, isn't it? Even with my Ma-non training,
I struggle to to to wrap my head around parts of it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0004
rows.name:
Well, every day is a learning experience, I suppose?
But I think whoever invented the mimeosome is a
certifiable genius![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0008
rows.name:
There's a Ma-non who hangs out on Division Drive
named Ackwar. Have you met him?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0009
rows.name:
He's super honest, don't you think? A true believer in
justice, that one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0010
rows.name:
Apparently he applied to become a Mediator and got
the job?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0011
rows.name:
I wish my little brother Sostenasa was more like him.
What is it you humans say? I would have fewer gray
hairs or...something?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0020
rows.name:
Did you know that every piece of Candid & Credible
protective wear is based on the actual Ma-non
space suits we use on our galactic travels?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0021
rows.name:
They are especially resilient against electromagnetic
raysâ€”which I think you generally refer to as electric
attacks?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0022
rows.name:
Well, if you ever need to to dodge lightning bolts
as some kind of weird training method...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0023
rows.name:
Well, I guess that's not very feasible, is it?
Still, our gear will certainly help prevent you from
getting burnt to to an electric crisp.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0012
rows.name: Did you hear the dreadful news about Ackwar?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0013
rows.name: Some criminal scoundrel murdered him, I guess?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0014
rows.name:
It's such a tragedy, isn't it? Ackwar was the kind of
Ma-non we all looked up to, and I wanted Sostenasa
to follow in his footsteps. But now...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0015
rows.name:
Well, maybe this is the low point in troubles between
your people and mine? Because I very much want to
to to believe that we can move past this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0016
rows.name:
Did you hear the wonderful news about Ackwar the
Mediator?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0017
rows.name:
Apparently he busted some kind of violent criminal!
It's a proud day for the Ma-non, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0018
rows.name: Perhaps Ackwar was born to be a Mediator...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev031201_MSG0019
rows.name:
I hope my little brother Sostenasa learns to be half
as honest and diligent as he is, you know?[ST:wait ]
